item.title: CVE-2021-21512|2024-09-17T00:56:16.036Z -- dell -- cyber%20recovery
item.description: Dell EMC PowerProtect Cyber Recovery, version 19.7.0.1, contains an Information Disclosure vulnerability. A locally authenticated high privileged Cyber Recovery user may potentially exploit this vulnerability leading to the takeover of the notification email account.
